title: The Left doesn't seem to have noticed that the Tories won the election
text: The Left doesn't seem to have noticed that the Tories won the election Saturday, 3 October 2015 (43 minutes ago) Telegraph View: Conservatives probably make up the silent majority of this country. But you wouldn't know it from the noisy protests in the streets
